    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How much does trash compactor repair cost in Los Angeles?</h3>
        <p>Diagnostic $89 waived with repair. Switch replacement $120–$200. Drive gear/chain $150–$250. Motor $200–$350. Most repairs are under $250. Written estimate before any work.</p>
